<HEADLINE>
NEW DEVELOPMENT WILL BE WIRED INTO INTERNET
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JASON Z. COHEN 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR; Valencia, Calif. _ Newhall Ranch will be wired for speed under
a deal between its developer, The Newhall Land &AMP; Farming Company,
and SBC Communications Inc., the parent company of Pacific Bell.
</P>
<P>
   The project will encompass 30,000 homes and thousands of
businesses, making Newhall Ranch and parts of Valencia the first
