month of March is the time to bring out all books related to
Ireland. Among this year's best is Terry Golway's ``For the Cause
of Liberty - A Thousand Years of Ireland's Heroes (Simon and
Schuster, $26, 335 pages). By BOBBIE HESS.
</P>
<P>
   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   SALTER-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ NASA scientists have discovered
a scary threat to the astronauts who will eventually embark on the
space agency's two-year mission to Mars. But there's a solution:
They'll have to take Martha Stewart with them. By STEPHANIE SALTER.
