   &UR; INTERNATIONAL &LR;  (``i'' code)
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO (Dateline to kum, Yugoslavia) _ Developments after U.S.
troops in Kosovo carried out raids on the strongholds of ethnic
Albanian guerrillas on Wednesday. By Carlotta Gall.
</P>
<P>
