<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    CLINTON: U.S. WILL NOT ACCEPT NUCLEAR PROGRAMS IN INDIA,
PAKISTAN
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (w) Washington categories.
 &HT;    By BOB DEANS 
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ President Clinton, preparing for a high stakes
