   The Adventures of Sebastian Cole &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Coping with an extended family situation rearranged by divorce,
a bright, energetic 17-year-old (Adrian Grenier) learns that his
stepfather, Hank (Clark Gregg), has decided to undergo sexual
reassignment and become a woman. Once again the family is
shattered, with hurt and enraged relatives scattering from England
to California.
</P>
<P>
   After some dislocation of his own, Sebastian settles down with
Hank, now Henrietta, resuming his tortured adolescence and capping
