<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-16 23:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9359 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s BC-RHODEN-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      03-16 0795
