<DOCNO> NYT20000316.0431 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-16 23:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9363 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-KELLY-OBIT-2TAKES-NYT     03-16 1085
